Release Information
===================

21.3.0rc1 (2021-03-24)
----------------------

Fixed
*****

* ``klio job test`` now respects the ``--config-file`` option.
* Fix effective config file handling for ``klio job profile``.


`Full Changelog <https://docs.klio.io/en/latest/reference/cli/changelog.html>`_.



